12044.text: [12044] link '9 10 11 12 13 w01](https://huggingface.co/prithivMLmods/Stark-Prompt-Extender/resolve/main/assets/1.png)\xa0 ## Prompt Extender\xa0 The "Prompt Extender" is a tool or concept that can be applied in various fields, from artificial intelligence to creative writing. Its primary function is to expand or elaborate on a given prompt or idea, providing additional context, details, or possibilities. \xa0 \xa0 Creative Writing: In storytelling, a prompt extender can help writers delve deeper into the world they\'re creating. For instance, if the initial prompt is "a lone astronaut stranded on a distant planet," the extender could add layers by detailing the alien flora and fauna, the astronaut\'s internal struggles, or the backstory of how they ended up stranded.\xa0' url: https://huggingface.co/prithivMLmods/Stark-Prompt-Extender-ONNX/blob/main/README.md?code=true#L9
